BG.name: Adventure Time: Hey Ice King why'd you steal our garbage?!!
BG.description: Finn and Jake wake up one morning to find their trash stolen by the Ice King! Jake couldn’t care less about half-eaten bananas and old chicken diapers – but when the Ice King uses these stolen goods to construct a Garbage Princess, our heroes embark on a fantastical adventure and teach him a lesson! Journey through the Land of Ooo in an offbeat adventure to discover perilous dungeons, unimaginable treasures, the true meaning of friendship, and never-ending fun! Adventure Time: Hey Ice King! Why’d you steal our garbage?!! is the first video game based on the radical, Emmy nominated Cartoon Network show about two close friends – Jake, a wise old dog with a big heart, and Finn, a silly kid who wants to become a great hero. Adventure Time show creator Pendleton Ward is heavily involved with the game creation, including the design of a brand new storyline, concept, and quests.

BE.name: Adventure Time: Hey Ice King why'd you steal our garbage?!!
BE.description: Parcours la Terre de Ooo lors d'un périple déjanté qui te conduira dans les profondeurs insondables de souterrains labyrinthiques aux moult dangers! Prépare-toi à t'amuser tous azimuts et à découvrir des trésors inimaginables ainsi que le véritable sens de l'amitié! Adventure Time: Hey Ice King! Why’d you steal our garbage?!! est le tout premier jeu vidéo inspiré de la série Adventure Time qui fait un malheur sur Cartoon Network! Nominé aux Emmy, ce dessin animé radicalement extrême suit les tribulations de Jake, un vieux toutou au grand cœur, et de Finn, un gamin un peu crétin qui rêve de devenir un héros légendaire. Pendleton Ward, le créateur de ce chef-d'œuvre télévisuel, a participé activement au développement de ce titre, et notamment à l'élaboration d'un nouveau concept, d'une intrigue inédite et de quêtes exclusives!

Adventure Time show creator Pendleton Ward is heavily involved with the game creation, including the design of a brand new storyline, concept, and quests.
